com.nolz3003

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nolz3003.Controller

  • public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
    The Controller class which observes the menu.fxml view.
    Author:
    Austin Nolz - The Controller class listens for user events and updates the view using the Product class. This Controller contains methods to initialize the database, initialize comboBox members, add new products to a database, and display that data to a TableView.
